| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4270 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78067e68-4bb0-5cc3-b0a4-5c88a6a7b890"
